{
  "texts": [
    "To preprocess the dataset of intestinal organoids, we first excluded dimethylsulfoxide control cells and cells labeled as tuft cells.",
    "Following, we removed genes with fewer than 50 counts, size normalized total and labeled counts, and identified the 2,000 most highly variable genes with scvelo.pp.filter_and_normalize.",
    "The neighbor graph was constructed based on 30 PCs and 30 neighbors.",
    "Finally, we computed first-order-smoothed labeled and total mRNA counts.",
    "Parameter estimation."
  ]
}